Handwritten Message on A2 Luxe Italian White Folded Cards w/White Envelope
Your Handwritten Message will be delivered using this foldover card, which has a luxurious weight and texture. Made in Italy, this Paper Source luxe white paper is a perfect soft white with 25% cotton. 
Folded size - 4 1/4" x 5 1/2"
